QuestData.Title: Quantity Over Quality
QuestData.Description: The demons of Felblaze Ingress are amassing at an exponential rate.$b$bWe must cull these invaders before they have enough demons to flank our forces at Illidari Stand.$b$bWill you join us in battle?
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay demons in the Felblaze Ingress.
QuestData.CompletionText: Demons that can summon other demons are not the kind of demons we should leave alive.
QuestData.RewardText: That should stall these demons for a time. We may need to return in the future to ensure they have not regrouped.
